videos.headline: Lawrence slings TD pass to Ladson
videos.description: Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence lasers a pass into the end zone and WR Frank Ladson Jr. makes the grab for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence slings TD pass to Ladson) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawrence calls his own number for another Clemson TD
videos.description: Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence keeps the ball himself and pushes two yards into the end zone for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence calls his own number for another Clemson TD) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clemson's Skalski elated after scoop-and-score TD
videos.description: Clemson LB James Skalski recovers a fumble, returns it for a touchdown and can't contain his excitement afterwards.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clemson’s Skalski elated after scoop-and-score TD) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Uiagalelei secures first career Clemson TD
videos.description: Clemson freshman QB D.J. Uiagalelei calls the sneak and gets across the goal line for his first touchdown with the Tigers.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Uiagalelei secures first career Clemson TD) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawrence tosses third TD of the first half
videos.description: Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence finds Frank Ladson Jr. in stride for a 54-yard touchdown play, giving Lawrence his third TD throw of the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence tosses third TD of the first half) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawrence's 4 TDs fuel Clemson's rout
videos.description: Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence, with assistance from his offensive line, throws for 168 yards and three TDs and adds one rushing score in the Tigers' rout of The Citadel Bulldogs.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Lawrence’s 4 TDs fuel Clemson’s rout) 2020/09/19 ESHEET SOTFULL
